<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Package Management on Mark Ridgwell | Notes</title><link>https://markridgwell.com/tags/package-management/</link><description>Recent content in Package Management on Mark Ridgwell | Notes</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><lastBuildDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2019 08:47:11 +0100</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://markridgwell.com/tags/package-management/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Linux</title><link>https://markridgwell.com/posts/linux/readme/</link><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2019 08:47:11 +0100</pubDate><guid>https://markridgwell.com/posts/linux/readme/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="linux">Linux&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="package-management">Package Management&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="debian-based">Debian based&lt;/h3>
&lt;h4 id="removing-unused-packages">Removing unused packages&lt;/h4>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">apt autoremove
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="arch-based">Arch based&lt;/h3>
&lt;h4 id="removing-unused-packages-1">Removing unused packages&lt;/h4>
&lt;p>List what is unused&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">pacman -Qdtq
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>Remove all unused&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">pacman -Qdtq &lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span> pacman -Rs -
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>Remove Multilib packages:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">pacman -R &lt;span class="sb">`&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nv">LANG&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>C pacman -Sl multilib &lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span> grep installed &lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span> cut -d &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39; &amp;#39;&lt;/span> -f 2&lt;span class="sb">`&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>Once done edit &lt;code>/etc/pacman.conf&lt;/code> and comment out the ``[multilib]` section&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="dynamic-dns-with-ddclient">Dynamic DNS with ddclient&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">sudo apt-get install ddclient libdata-validate-ip-perl libjson-any-perl net-tools
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>Edit /etc/ddclient.conf as:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">daemon=1800
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">syslog=yes
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">protocol=cloudflare
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">use=web
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">web=checkip.dyndns.org/ 6
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">web-skip=‘IP Address’
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">ssl=yes
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">login=&amp;lt;Cloudflare Login&amp;gt;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">password=&amp;lt;APIKEY&amp;gt;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">zone=example.com
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">host.example.com
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>Verify config&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">sudo service ddclient status
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">sudo ddclient -query
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">sudo ddclient -daemon&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="m">0&lt;/span> -verbose -noquiet
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>Enable Service&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">sudo service ddclient status
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="set-hostname">Set Hostname&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">sudo hostnamectl set-hostname whatever.example.com
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="correct-keyboard-layout">Correct Keyboard layout&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://gist.github.com/keckelt/0ba90f8840e2903bfdc54c7e19ad4613">See&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">xmodmap -e &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;keycode 49 = grave&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div></description></item></channel></rss>